snippet.title: Bionicle - The Legend of Mata Nui BETA gameplay
snippet.description:
Some quick gameplay and (sadly) a crash from the recently made public version of the cancelled Bionicle PC game from 2001.

If you'd like to try it yourself you can download it from the Biomedia website 
http://biomediaproject.com/bmp/blog/the-legend-of-mata-nui-final-build/
